OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLewis Capaldi calls off    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftour after Glastonbury set 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lewis Capaldi has said he will take a  
OL,6, break from touring for the "foreseeable
OL,7, future", days after he struggled to    
OL,8, finish his Glastonbury set.            
OL,10,FThe Scottish singer, who has Tourette's
OL,11,FSyndrome, asked fans to help him by    
OL,12,Fsinging along at the festival.         
OL,14,FGlastonbury was the 26-year-old's first
OL,15,Flive performance since taking a        
OL,16,Fprevious three-week break.             
OL,18,FBut he said it "became obvious that I  
OL,19,Fneed to spend much more time getting my
OL,20,Fmental and physical health in order".  
